title: PIER / CINDY BARKS
description: Barks for Cindy the skull for when you haven't talked to her *AND* you're approaching her from below.

dialogueTree.title: Cindy the SKULL: ""Hey, up here, piggo!""
Cindy the SKULL: ""Yeah, you better keep walking.""
Cindy the SKULL: ""Look at me when I'm talking to you.""
dialogueTree.text: "Look at me when I'm talking to you."
